data.description: Stunning Mountain Views Surround this Fantastic Custom Contemporary Home in Beautiful Red Creek Ranch! Come Enjoy this quiet and tranquil setting on 40 acres. Trees, Mountains, and Wildlife are abundant!  Large Deck with Hot Tub so you can soak it all in.  Fabulous Floor plan features Main Level Master and Main Level laundry, Large, Open Great Room with Volume Ceilings,Wood floors, Dining Room with Pellet Stove and Gas Log fireplace in living room. Large Gourmet kitchen with double ovens, built-in desk area, center island with gas cooktop, plenty of cabinets.  Large main level Master has a  5 piece bath, large corner tub with separate shower.  3 additional main level bedrooms and bath  plus a huge loft could become additional bedrooms or an awesome game room, TV room, etc... 3rd bath is upstairs. Huge windows in every room take advantage of the magnificent views in every direction and provide passive solar heat in winter!  You really have to see this home to appreciate it!  2 car garage plus carport  Well permit #191963
